snippet.title: Dholida Dhol Re Vagade DJ Remix | Trending Gujarati Garba Song of Navratri 2025 | Dandiya Night Hits
snippet.description:

Welcome to Ishtar Gujarati, your ultimate destination for the best Gujarati songs, Garba hits, Navratri special tracks, and devotional music. This Navratri 2025, we bring you the all-time favorite and most energetic Gujarati Garba song ‚Äì ‚ÄúDholida Dhol Re Vagade‚Äù. Known for its powerful beats, traditional vibes, and festive spirit, this song has become a must-play at every Garba ground, Dandiya night, and Navratri celebration.

#DholidaDholReVagade #GujaratiGarba #IshtarGujarati #Navratri2025 #GarbaSongs #DandiyaNight #GujaratiSong #NavratriSpecial #GarbaDance #TrendingGarba #djremix 

‚ú® About the Song
Dholida Dhol Re Vagade is one of the most loved Gujarati Garba tracks that captures the true essence of Navratri celebrations. With its rhythmic dhol beats and soulful Gujarati lyrics, it creates the perfect atmosphere for Garba lovers across the globe. Whether you are in Ahmedabad, Surat, Vadodara, Rajkot, or celebrating Navratri internationally in the USA, UK, Canada, or Australia ‚Äì this song unites Gujaratis everywhere in devotion and dance.

‚ú® Why This Song is Perfect for Navratri 2025

Energetic Garba beats that make everyone dance.

A trending Navratri song that‚Äôs loved by both youth and elders.

Ideal for Dandiya competitions, Garba nights, and cultural events.

Brings alive the spirit of Maa Durga‚Äôs blessings through music and rhythm.

One of the most requested Gujarati Garba songs on dance floors during Navratri.

‚ú® Celebrate Navratri with Ishtar Gujarati
At Ishtar Gujarati, we aim to bring you not just songs, but memories and traditions through music. Our channel is home to:

Traditional Gujarati Garba songs üéµ

Latest Navratri 2025 Dandiya hits üíÉ

Folk songs from Gujarat üå∏

Devotional bhajans and Mataji songs üôè

Festival special music playlists üåü

‚ú® Dholida Dhol Re Vagade ‚Äì A Song of Tradition & Energy
Garba is not just a dance, it is an emotion for Gujaratis. From kids to elders, everyone circles around the garba ground to celebrate the victory of good over evil during Navratri. The beats of Dholida Dhol Re Vagade fill every heart with joy, reminding us of our roots and culture. The track is timeless and continues to be a favorite Garba anthem year after year.

‚ú® Global Gujarati Celebration
This song is not limited to Gujarat alone. During Navratri 2025, Gujarati communities worldwide celebrate with Garba and Dandiya events. From New Jersey to London, Toronto to Sydney, Dholida Dhol Re Vagade will echo in Garba halls, temples, and cultural gatherings.

‚ú® How to Enjoy This Song

Play it loud during your Navratri Garba nights.

Add it to your Dandiya playlist for festive vibes.

Share it with friends and family to spread the joy.

Use it as background music for your Navratri reels and shorts.

‚ú® Ishtar Gujarati ‚Äì Your Navratri Music Partner
We at Ishtar Gujarati are committed to delivering high-quality music for every Gujarati household. Our mission is to keep traditions alive by offering you timeless folk, trending Garba songs, and devotional tracks that connect with your heart and soul.

üôè Blessings of Maa Durga
This Navratri, let the blessings of Maa Durga bring prosperity, happiness, and positivity in your life. Dance your heart out to Dholida Dhol Re Vagade and keep the festive spirit alive.

snippet.title: OG Trailer Telugu #TheyCallHimOG  | Pawan Kalyan | Emraan Hashmi | Sujeeth | Thaman S | DVV Danayya
snippet.description:
Now see the other side of the play for #OG

#TheyCallHimOG on September 25th

Cast - Pawan Kalyan, Emraan Hashmi, Priyanka Arul Mohan, Arjun Das, Sriya Reddy, Prakash Raj
Movie Name: They Call Him OG
Written & Directed by Sujeeth
Music by Thaman S
Production: DVV Entertainment
Presented by: Smt D.Parvathi
Produced by DVV Danayya, Kalyan Dasari
Cinematographers : Ravi K Chandran (ISC), Manoj Paramahamsa (ISC)
Production Designer : AS Prakash
Editor: Navin Nooli
Costume Designers: Darshan Jalan & Neelanchal Kumar Ghosh
Action Masters : A Vijay, Peter Hein, Dhilip Subbarayan, Kevin Kumar, Stunt Silva, Sunil Rodrigues, Kecha Khampakdee, Juji, Supreme Sundar, Jashwa, Parvez
Co-director: Somaraju PVV
Direction Department : Uday Alla, Aarun Thevar, Lokesh Srinivasan, Kishore Sarella,
Kedar Pashikanti, Durga D.R, Sainadh Alla, Mithilesh Sivagani, Rithica Devireddy,
 I.Chaitanya Sravanth, N.Sruti Ranjani, RSN.Roshan Sharif
Creative Producer : Harish Pai
Chief Associate Editors : Raam tumu, Srinu Bainaboyina
Associate Editors : Prashanth Tej, Yogi (D.F.Tech), Vishnu ramagiri
Executive Producer: Sathyanarayana Guggilla
Production Controller: Manikanta Rongala
Sound Design : Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tammareddy
Stills : Mallesh Thatha
Creative Director : Ashwin Mani
Marketing: Walls and Trends
PRO: Venugopal
DI : Annapurna Studios
Teaser cut : Vishnu Ramagiri
Audio on: Sony Music

Lyrics: 
CHAAYI HAI TABAAHI
NAAM HAI USKA OMI
ZULMAT NA KHAMOSHI
RAAKH KAREGA OMI

GUNS AND ROSES
THEY GONNA BE VICIOUS
THE DEVIL COLOURED GLASSES
OH THEY SHOW YOU THE BRUISES

GUNS AND ROSES
WEAKER ONE LOSES
GANGSTA COMING WALKING
THROUGH THE FIRESTORM RAGES

CHAAYI HAI TABAAHI
NAAM HAI USKA OMI
ZULMAT NA KHAMOSHI
RAAKH KAREGA OMI

Music Credits :
Music : Thaman S
Programmed & Arranged by - Thaman S
Beat & EDM works - Beyond Sound (T) 
Electric Rhythm - Thaman S
Electric Guitars - Subhashree 
Additional Programming - Shashank Alamuru Osho V & Hari S R

Lyrics : Adviteeya Vojjala
Rap: Harsha Darivemula 
Chorus: Adviteeya, Pranati, Sruthika, Pratyusha, Girija & Soujanya

Recorded at V Studios ( Chn ) by Osho V & Hari @ Vibe ( HYD )
Vocal Supervision - Adviteeya
Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge ( Mumbai )
Assistant engineers -  Jazbaat, Sohamm, Prasad

Musicians Co Ordinator - Manikandan K
Studio Manager - Seenu & Sridhar
Studio Assistance - Raju, Kannan, Lingam & Pawan
